\ul Regarding the Exam Pattern:\ulnone\par
The Exam is for 1 1/2 Hours, in which 1 Hour is given for 10 Puzzles to solve, and the Remaining 1/2 an Hour is given to answer 45 Simple English Grammar Questions. There's no Need to Worry about the English. It'll be Quite Easy.\par
\ul Regarding Puzzles & English:\ulnone\par
